          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-game-green flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Full multiplayer support</strong>: Co-op play, invite codes, and online sessions work perfectly.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- App Info Grid -->
      <AppInfoGrid />

      <!-- Main Content Sections -->
      <div class="prose-game">
        <h2 id="what-is">What is Super Bear Adventure? (A 90s Inspired Masterpiece)</h2>
        <p>
          Super Bear Adventure is a 3D platformer that feels like late 90s classics such as Banjo-Kazooie and Super Mario 64. You play as Baaren, a brave bear exploring the Kingdom of Earthkwak to save his friends from a toxic purple honey. The official game includes daily challenges, speedy vehicles, and fun mini-games in the Arcade World—our mod keeps all of that and removes ads and grind. For the full story, read our <a href="/blog/lore-baaren-story/">complete breakdown of the Kingdom of Earthkwak lore</a>.
        </p>

        <h3>A True 3D Platforming Experience</h3>
        <p>
          Unlike most mobile platformers that rely on 2D side-scrolling, Super Bear Adventure gives you full 3D freedom. You can run, jump, climb, swim, and even drive vehicles across massive open-world environments. The game's physics engine allows for creative movement techniques like wall jumps, speed boosts, and hidden shortcuts that speedrunners love. Learn all the advanced techniques in our <a href="/blog/how-to-play-beginner-guide/">beginner guide</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 id="official-apk-vs-mod">Official Super Bear Adventure APK vs Mod APK</h2>
        <p>
          Understanding the difference helps you choose the right version. The official game on Google Play has over 100M+ downloads and a 4.4-star rating with 883K+ reviews. It's free but includes ads and requires grinding for coins to unlock cosmetics.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
          <strong>Official app on Play Store:</strong> 100M+ downloads, 4.4★ (883K+ reviews), PEGI 3. Store listing updated {SITE.download.updated}. Developer: <a href="https://earthkwak.games/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Earthkwak Games</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Comparison Table -->
      <ComparisonTable />

      <div class="prose-game">
        <h2 id="evolution">The Evolution of the Kingdom: 2024 vs 2026 Comparison</h2>
        <p>
          Comparing the <a href="/blog/super-bear-adventure-mod-apk-old-versions/">older versions archive</a> to the current build shows how far Earthkwak has taken the Kingdom of Earthkwak—from Update 10.0's <strong>The Hive</strong> (2022) to Update 12.0's <strong>multiplayer</strong> (2025) and the 12.1.x polish patches in 2026. The April 2026 v12.1.5 release is small but important for online play; major content drops were 12.1.0 (emotes, Super Bear Fighters) and 12.0.0 (co-op).
        </p>

