        <ul>
          <li><strong>Multiplayer invite code fix</strong> — Invite codes now work reliably across all regions</li>
          <li><strong>Performance improvements</strong> — Smoother framerate on mid-range devices</li>
          <li><strong>Bug fixes</strong> — Several crash fixes in The Hive and Mole Mines</li>
          <li><strong>UI polish</strong> — Updated menus and loading screens</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For the complete history, see our <a href="/blog/version-changelogs/">version changelog archive</a>.</p>

        <h2 id="exclusive-features">Exclusive Mod Features</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-6 not-prose">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-yellow-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Unlimited Coins & Gems</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Start with unlimited currency to buy anything instantly</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-purple-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M7 7h.01M7 3h5c.512 0 1.024.195 1.414.586l7 7a2 2 0 010 2.828l-7 7a2 2 0 01-2.828 0l-7-7A1.994 1.994 0 013 12V7a4 4 0 014-4z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">All Skins & Hats Unlocked</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Access every cosmetic item from day one</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">No Advertisements</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Play without interruptions — zero ads</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-5 shadow-sm">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-green-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Anti-Ban Protection</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Play safely with built-in protection</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 id="six-worlds">The 6 Massive Worlds</h2>
        <p>Super Bear Adventure features six unique open-world environments, each with its own theme, enemies, secrets, and collectibles:</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 my-6 not-prose">
          {[
            { name: 'Turtletown', desc: 'Your starting hub — a peaceful town with hidden areas and friendly NPCs.', color: 'bg-green-500', href: '/blog/turtletown-walkthrough/' },
            { name: 'Snow Valley', desc: 'Icy peaks with snowboard sections and frozen puzzles.', color: 'bg-blue-500', href: '/blog/snow-valley-secrets/' },
            { name: 'Beemothep Desert', desc: 'Ancient ruins, sand traps, and sphinx-inspired puzzles.', color: 'bg-amber-500', href: '/blog/beemothep-desert-puzzle/' },
            { name: 'Giant House', desc: 'Everything is oversized — navigate a world where you are tiny.', color: 'bg-orange-500', href: '/blog/giant-house-walkthrough/' },
            { name: 'The Hive', desc: 'A buzzing bee kingdom with honey-themed obstacles.', color: 'bg-yellow-500', href: '/blog/the-hive-walkthrough/' },
            { name: 'Mole Mines', desc: 'Underground caverns with mining carts and gem puzzles.', color: 'bg-stone-500', href: '/blog/mole-mines-walkthrough/' },
          ].map((world) => (
            <a href={world.href} class="block bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-4 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all">
              <div class:list={['w-full h-24 rounded-lg mb-3 flex items-center justify-center', world.color]}>
                <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">{world.name}</span>
              </div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 text-sm mb-1">{world.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-600">{world.desc}</p>
            </a>
          ))}
        </div>

        <h2 id="install">How to Download and Install</h2>
        <div class="my-6 space-y-4 not-prose">
          {installSteps.map((step, i) => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-100 p-5 shadow-sm">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-game-green text-white font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-lg">
                {i + 1}
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">{step.name}</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">{step.text}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="text-center my-8">
          <a href={SITE.download.url} class="btn-download">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4" />
            </svg>
            Download Super Bear Adventure Mod APK v{SITE.download.version}
          </a>
        </div>

        <h2 id="mod-safe">Is the Mod Safe?</h2>
        <p>
          Yes. Our mod APK is built from the official v{SITE.download.version} base. It has been scanned with multiple antivirus engines and contains no malware, spyware, or trojans. No root access is required, and it does not access any personal data beyond what the official game normally uses.
        </p>

        <h2 id="optimization">Optimization for Low-End Devices</h2>
        <p>
          If you experience lag or frame drops, check our <a href="/blog/lag-fix-optimization/">optimization guide</a>. The mod includes all the same graphics settings as the official game, so you can lower quality for smoother performance on older devices. Key tips:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Lower graphics quality in Settings</li>
          <li>Close background apps before playing</li>
          <li>Enable battery saver mode for consistent performance</li>
          <li>Clear app cache periodically</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 id="final-verdict">Final Verdict & Conclusion</h2>
        <p>
          Super Bear Adventure Mod APK v{SITE.download.version} is the definitive way to experience one of the best 3D platformers on mobile. With unlimited coins, all cosmetics unlocked, no ads, and full multiplayer support, you get the complete experience without the grind. Whether you're a returning player or discovering the Kingdom of Earthkwak for the first time, the mod gives you everything you need to dive right in and explore.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Ready to start?</strong> Download the mod from the button above and begin your adventure. For questions, visit our <a href="/faq/">FAQ page</a> or <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ Section -->
      <FAQAccordion items={faqItems} />
    </article>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
